metadata.name: Buffies #1
metadata.description: Buffies are a collection of randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockhain with a total supply of 5555. Buffies belong to the Buffieverse. Our vision is to amplify the people of the metaverse with a healthy and unique lifestyle. Buffies are first PERMAMENT metaverse skin, all Buffie owners will be getting free 3D models of Buffies. Buffies will also be the first NFT to mine Altcoins! Check the whitepaper on the website for more info!
